 :success-metrics
 ["Users can distinguish agent bugs from their own issues"
  "Clear path to report bugs to correct vendor"
  "Reduced confusion when tasks 'fail' after completing work"
  "Better error analytics for identifying systemic issues"]

 :future-enhancements
 ["Automatic error reporting to vendors (with user consent)"
